Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_phy::_lane1_rx_lbert_err

PHY LANE1 RX LBERT Error. A read of this register, or a SYNC from the RX LBERT Control register resets the error count. If all bits in this regisert are set, the error counter has saturated.
